				<li class="pull_right"><a href="http://twitter.com/slinggit" title="Twitter" class="twitIcon_dark" >Twitter</a></li>
				<li class="pull_right"><a href="http://blog.slinggit.com/" title="Blog" class="slinggitIcon">Blog</a></li>
